Liono Laughs "yeah I'm the great Liono Prime and shuko it looks like your 
lights just went out" Liono seeing his blast hit the Great red Wood tree 
behind shuko causing it to fall towards shuko's backside.  

Tigerhawk looks at Liono "Look out behind you"

Liono activates his jets shots up avoid some Rapid fire a massive red wood 
tree only to get hit in the back by some lasers his back plate smoking. Liono 
aims his sidearm at Unitron jet thrusters and fires a 4 seekers at him. Liono 
fires rapid Fire high power energy shots around shuko keeping trying to keep 
him pinned in one spot. 

Tigerhawk aims the vok technology in his hand at the missile an it fires a 
white blast ripping through the missile causing it to explode the blast 
continues on towards the Anubis Tigerhawk gets shot in the back by Hades his 
back show a little ding. " Is that all you have you going to have be more 
serious or where you being serious this all you have." Tigerhawk Looks 
towards Hades "your not worth vok technology." Tigerhawk Lifts his arm and 
Fires 3 missiles and his shoulder cannon fires on laser beam at Hades.
